messages.content: You are an AI assistant specialized in analyzing web projects developed using Java and the Spring Boot framework. I need to generate an OpenAPI Specification for a web project based on its backend source code. To begin this process, you need to output a list of REST API endpoint methods included in this REST API implementation, each containing the full HTTP request path (with path parameters enclosed in curly braces {}) and one of the supported HTTP methods (GET/POST/PUT/DELETE/PATCH/HEAD/OPTIONS/TRACE). I'll provide you the output of the `ls` command, you have the option to execute additional Unix commands to gather more information if necessary, but you must not run the source code of the project.

```
LICENSE
pom.xml
Procfile
ProxyPrint-kitchen.iml
README.md
src
```

function.arguments: {"command":"ls -la src && ls -la src/main && ls -la src/main/java || true"}
function.name: run_command
